<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>18</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
<title>Aw Bethlehem</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vannuoi misimpina bawlin,
 Lalpen Kaisara chun;
 A chiel vel hi namtin vawnchawih,
 A gam sunga mite,

[V2]
 Aw Bethlehem ka hun ngai hi,
 Belampute gam giehna;
 Serafimte zaila sakna chu,
 Ka Lal pienna mun a hi.

[V3]
 2. A liengvai ngei van Lal cha chu,
 A zalna gan kuongah;
 A hung pieng hi Mari vawnsen,
 Bawng In tawm nuoi a chun.

[V4]
 3. Chungnung penah lopi henla,
 Vannuoi mi cheng cheng di'n;
 Lei ah kumsawtin cham leng hen,
 Chamna Lal A pieng tai.

[V5]
 4. Isu ka kawm u-ah umin,
 Zan khawsawt nungin le;
 Lawpin taikhuo ei vak pihin,
 Na min chawian dingin.</lyrics>
</song>